# SSH gateway
Host citrix-gate
Hostname gate.ctxuk.citrix.com
User simonbe
IdentityFile = ~/.ssh/personal-id_rsa
Compression no
ServerAliveInterval 123
ForwardAgent yes
ForwardX11 yes
ForwardX11Timeout 1d
TCPKeepAlive yes
LocalForward 3389 simonbe-xenia:3389
DynamicForward localhost:1080
